{"fadein":1.5,"once":true,"id":"AIMIER1","fadeType":2,"mode":2,"fadeOut":1.5,"scripts":[{"mode":1,"sequence":[["Émile, the Dancing Angel\n\n<size=45>Chapter 1 - The Popular Dancer<\/size>",1]],"stopbgm":true},{"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"flashin":{"black":true,"delay":1,"dur":1,"alpha":[1,0]},"side":2,"bgm":"story-1","say":"Port - Dock","dir":1,"bgmDelay":2,"flashout":{"black":true,"dur":1,"alpha":[0,1]}},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"My newly appointed secretary, Émile Bertin, and I were waiting on a commission team's return.","dir":1},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"The cloudless blue sky, the warm and bright rays of the sun – ah, what a wonderful day~","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":802010},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"And on such a wonderful day, it'd be a shame not to go outside and move around~","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":802010},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"Émile jumped onto a bollard and did a graceful pirouette.","dir":1},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Really, you ought to get more exercise, Commander! Going outside only to greet returning commission teams is not enough.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":802010},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Of course, work is important, but sitting too much is bad for the body.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":802010},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"And the work you do, dear me, it seems really tough~ I'm doing the best I can just to keep up!","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":802010},{"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"options":[{"flag":1,"content":"Respond humbly"},{"flag":2,"content":"Respond boastfully"}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","dir":1,"say":"People who become commanders really are on a whole other level~","actor":802010},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Ah, look, there they are!","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":802010},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"The commission team all gathered around Émile like it was routine. They had a cheery girls' talk about their commission accomplishments and rewards.","dir":1},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"......","dir":1},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Well done! You didn't have any close calls, did you?","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":802010},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"......","dir":1},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"But of course I would worry about your wellbeing! You're my dear friends!","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":802010},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"......","dir":1},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Ah, is this for me? You're too sweet! Merci!","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":802010},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"......","dir":1},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Commander, is something the matter? You seem taken aback.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":802010},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"... Oh, this? We're all part of the same fleet, so shouldn't we try our best to make friends with each other?","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":802010},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"Apparently, Émile doesn't realize how popular she really is.","blackBg":true,"dir":1}]}